  <div class="modal-content glass-card" style="max-width:700px;max-height:80vh;overflow-y:auto">
    <div class="modal-header">
      <h2>📖 单词收藏本</h2>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:center">
        <button class="btn btn-small" id="vocabImportBtn">📥 导入</button>
        <button class="btn btn-small" id="vocabExportImgBtn">🖼 批量成图</button>
        <button class="popup-close" id="vocabModalClose">✕</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
      <div class="vocab-grid" id="vocabGrid"></div>
      <div id="vocabEmpty" style="text-align:center;color:var(--text-dim);padding:40px">
        还没有收藏单词，点击字幕中的单词后点 ☆ 收藏
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
```

#### styles.css additions (~40 lines)

```css
/* 收藏按钮 */
.btn-fav {
  padding: 6px 14px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text);
  background: rgba(255,200,50,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(255,200,50,0.3);
