### Feature 2: 批量单词成图 (Batch Word-to-Image)

#### main.js additions (~15 lines)

```javascript
// IPC: AI grouping words
ipcMain.handle('ai-group-words', async (_, words) => {
  const prompt = `将以下单词按语义相关性分组，每组5-20个词，输出JSON数组格式 [[group1words],[group2words],...]，不要其他内容：\n${words.join(', ')}`;
  const result = await callAI(prompt);
  try { return JSON.parse(result.match(/\[[\s\S]*\]/)?.[0] || '[]'); }
  catch(e) { return [words]; }
});

// IPC: AI generate scene description for a word group
ipcMain.handle('ai-scene-desc', async (_, words) => {
  const prompt = `为以下单词组生成一个简短的场景描述（一句话，用于配图背景），单词：${words.join(', ')}。只回复场景描述。`;
  return await callAI(prompt);
});
```

